LOTUS PHARMACEUT said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 1.01% to NT$37,013,000 from NT$36,644,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales             37,013           36,644    
YOY%              1.01%    -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            215,994          233,117    
YOY%              -7.35% 
=================================================================
 